<c.bg_transparent>How much do you know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about carbon reaction chambers?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:02.513 --> 00:07:04.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've learned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little about laser-induced fusion</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:04.751 --> 00:07:05.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>not much more than the basics.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:06.112 --> 00:07:07.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, it's a bloody inefficient system.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:07:08.190 --> 00:07:10.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd trade it in for a Federation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>model tomorrow if I could</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:10.630 --> 00:07:11.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it's all we've got.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:12.149 --> 00:07:12.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do me a favor.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:13.269 --> 00:07:15.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep an eye on the exhaust</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>plasma temperature.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:17.748 --> 00:07:22.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, increase deuterium flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by five percent to reaction chamber two.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:22.706 --> 00:07:24.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Procedure is not recommended.</i></c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:24.625 --> 00:07:26.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I've had enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your opinions, damn it.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:27.255 --> 00:07:27.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just do it!</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:28.648 --> 00:07:29.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Procedure is not recommended.</i></c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:29.704 --> 00:07:35.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Consult Cardassian operational guidelines</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>paragraph 254-A, now on screen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:35.383 --> 00:07:39.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to read your tech manual.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Fine. We'll do it ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:42.261 --> 00:07:43.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reinitializing reactor two.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:45.140 --> 00:07:49.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Directing plasma flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to conduits 143, 144...</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:49.979 --> 00:07:51.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien, the power</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>flow from reactor two</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:07:52.183 --> 00:07:52.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has just been shut down.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:53.576 --> 00:07:53.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:54.577 --> 00:07:57.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze reactor two failure.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:57.536 --> 00:08:00.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Reactor two was shut down</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>after sensors detected</i></c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:00.335 --> 00:08:03.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>a potential overload</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of the carbon reaction chambers.</i></c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:04.143 --> 00:08:05.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it. That's the straw!</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:05.694 --> 00:08:07.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relax, Chief. It's just a computer.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:08.928 --> 00:08:11.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is no computer. This is my archenemy.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:11.251 --> 00:08:13.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got it working just fine,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as far I can tell.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:13.171 --> 00:08:15.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine? With all due respect, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:15.810 --> 00:08:17.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As an engineer,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I couldn't look at myself in the mirror</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:17.730 --> 00:08:21.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>if I allowed this computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to continue to perform as it is now.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:21.369 --> 00:08:22.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to do a root canal.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:22.928 --> 00:08:23.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Root canal?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:23.888 --> 00:08:27.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's engineering shorthand, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to get into its guts.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:27.876 --> 00:08:29.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-and rebuild it from the ground up.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How long will that take?</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:30.707 --> 00:08:32.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm still not that familiar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Cardassian technology</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:32.365 --> 00:08:35.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, oh, I guess no more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than two, three years.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:35.684 --> 00:08:39.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's going to take a lot of man-hours.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Is it really necessary?</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:08:39.835 --> 00:08:40.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand--</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:08:40.443 --> 00:08:43.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's just say I don't have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your sensitivity to the computer.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:08:44.242 --> 00:08:45.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's all right. Forget about it.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:08:45.961 --> 00:08:47.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Uh, Chief...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's all right. It doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:08:47.801 --> 00:08:50.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, I want you to do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:08:51.559 --> 00:08:53.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, sir. I'll get right on it.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:08:54.998 --> 00:08:59.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And this is Ops.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The heart and soul of Deep Space 9.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:08:59.557 --> 00:09:00.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, there you are, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:01.877 --> 00:09:03.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gentlemen, Madam Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:04.276 --> 00:09:06.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They insisted on seeing operations, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:06.875 --> 00:09:07.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:08.434 --> 00:09:11.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Make yourselves at home.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I trust that Doctor Bashir</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:11.754 --> 00:09:13.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has been taking care of all your needs.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:14.330 --> 00:09:17.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he refuses to change</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my accommodations.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:17.472 --> 00:09:18.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Accommodations?</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:18.672 --> 00:09:21.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if I have to sleep another night</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:21.310 --> 00:09:24.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a Cardassian bed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with gargoyles staring at me</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:24.470 --> 00:09:25.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from the wood poles...</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:25.910 --> 00:09:26.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:27.389 --> 00:09:29.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>An unidentified vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:30.691 --> 00:09:31.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen. Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:32.987 --> 00:09:34.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, you'll get a better view</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from over here.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:09:43.584 --> 00:09:45.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quite a sight isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:09:46.343 --> 00:09:48.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it? That's the whole thing?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:09:49.503 --> 00:09:50.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, yes, it is.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:09:50.942 --> 00:09:52.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was expecting more, somehow.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:09:52.981 --> 00:09:55.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Scanners aren't picking up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any life-forms on board.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:09:56.206 --> 00:09:58.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-A probe?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Might be.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:09:58.660 --> 00:10:00.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading an extensive computer array</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:00.779 --> 00:10:03.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but no signals to suggest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's trying to maintain contact</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:03.178 --> 00:10:04.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with a mother ship.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:04.458 --> 00:10:06.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are the computers compatible with ours?</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:06.897 --> 00:10:08.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's hard to tell.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:08.216 --> 00:10:11.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't recognize any known</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>subprocessor patterns.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:11.336 --> 00:10:13.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obviously, the young woman</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doesn't have the necessary experience.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:13.775 --> 00:10:14.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps I can--</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:14.774 --> 00:10:19.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The "young woman" over there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has over 300 years experience, Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:19.134 --> 00:10:22.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: I might have better luck</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we towed it into the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:22.573 --> 00:10:25.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, not until we know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little bit more about it.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:25.491 --> 00:10:27.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, tow it to 500 meters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>off the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:27.971 --> 00:10:28.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:10:29.114 --> 00:10:31.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. O'Brien, try to set up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>an adaptive interface link</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:10:31.330 --> 00:10:33.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and see if we can download</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any information from it.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:10:33.649 --> 00:10:34.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:10:36.928 --> 00:10:40.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it will be best</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we clear this area.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:10:40.407 --> 00:10:43.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But this probe may represent contact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a new species.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:10:43.446 --> 00:10:45.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, I think it would be appropriate</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:10:45.126 --> 00:10:48.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for at least one Federation ambassador</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be present at this historic occasion</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:10:48.605 --> 00:10:52.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and since I have a particular interest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in First Contact procedures...</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:10:52.164 --> 00:10:53.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate your interest, Ambassador</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:10:54.163 --> 00:10:57.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to keep you all informed,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm scheduling a briefing</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:10:57.827 --> 00:11:01.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>at 0400. In the meantime, Dr. Bashir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the best place to view this probe</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:01.721 --> 00:11:03.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is from the docking ring near Port Seven.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:06.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll show them the way.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:16.196 --> 00:11:17.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:29.433 --> 00:11:31.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such concentration.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:11:31.951 --> 00:11:34.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such intensity, such passion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for your work.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:11:35.511 --> 00:11:37.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tracking intergalactic malefactors.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:11:39.429 --> 00:11:41.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Most people find it rather tedious.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:11:41.869 --> 00:11:44.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tedious? ( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:11:44.148 --> 00:11:47.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, those of us who have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>beneficiaries of your heroism</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:11:48.146 --> 00:11:49.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>would never call your work tedious.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:11:50.706 --> 00:11:52.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've learned that, on this station</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:11:52.585 --> 00:11:56.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you are the thin, beige line</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between order and chaos.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:11:57.744 --> 00:11:58.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's my job.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:11:59.943 --> 00:12:04.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, what can I do for you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You haven't lost anything else, I hope.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:05.382 --> 00:12:06.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only my heart.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:07.541 --> 00:12:08.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I beg your pardon?</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:12:09.781 --> 00:12:10.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is, um...</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:11.579 --> 00:12:13.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is Odo your first or last name?</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:12:15.591 --> 00:12:15.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:12:16.984 --> 00:12:18.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh. Then I can just call you, uh?</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:12:19.177 --> 00:12:19.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:12:21.377 --> 00:12:23.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It has a certain lyrical quality.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:24.936 --> 00:12:25.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lyrical?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:26.255 --> 00:12:27.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo...</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:27.815 --> 00:12:29.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It rolls off the tongue.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:12:30.854 --> 00:12:31.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:12:32.374 --> 00:12:34.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have a lot of work to do.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:12:35.413 --> 00:12:37.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand you're a shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:12:38.126 --> 00:12:38.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's correct.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:12:38.972 --> 00:12:40.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never been with a shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:12:42.651 --> 00:12:43.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Been with?"</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:12:44.450 --> 00:12:46.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've heard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you're the only one of your kind.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:12:48.649 --> 00:12:49.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So far.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:12:50.808 --> 00:12:53.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm. All the men I've known</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:12:53.447 --> 00:12:56.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have needed to be shaped,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and molded, and manipulated</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:12:56.846 --> 00:12:58.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and finally I've met a man</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:12:58.806 --> 00:13:00.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who knows how to do it himself.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:13:02.245 --> 00:13:03.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:13:04.684 --> 00:13:07.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning ) Is that the com?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I think it is. Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:13:07.643 --> 00:13:08.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got to get to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:13:25.558 --> 00:13:30.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Initiating high-resolution scan.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Memory nodes located.</i></c.bg_transparent>

233
00:13:30.636 --> 00:13:32.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Proceeding with data transfer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

234
00:13:33.355 --> 00:13:35.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, there you go.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Who would have thought?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:13:35.914 --> 00:13:36.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seem surprised, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:13:37.514 --> 00:13:38.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, knowing this computer,</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:13:38.953 --> 00:13:41.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought I would have had to reconfigure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the whole emulator module</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:13:41.273 --> 00:13:45.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to make it compatible with the probe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's cooperating for once.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:13:46.591 --> 00:13:48.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Transfer of data is complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

240
00:13:49.390 --> 00:13:50.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well done, computer.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:13:51.829 --> 00:13:55.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, run standard code translations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on probe data.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:13:55.269 --> 00:13:56.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isolate syntax results.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:13:57.268 --> 00:13:58.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Processing.</i></c.bg_transparent>

244
00:13:58.547 --> 00:13:59.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:03.746 --> 00:14:05.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in. Yes, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:05.785 --> 00:14:06.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander...</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:14:07.785 --> 00:14:09.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I have a problem.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark again?</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:09.745 --> 00:14:12.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, sir. This one is named Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:12.904 --> 00:14:14.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lwaxana Troi, the ambassador?</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:14:14.903 --> 00:14:15.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's her.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:16.303 --> 00:14:20.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was a minor incident at the bar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I helped her with, and now she's...</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:14:21.861 --> 00:14:22.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Grateful.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:14:23.540 --> 00:14:24.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's the problem?</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:14:25.139 --> 00:14:28.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The manner in which</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she expresses her... gratitude.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:14:29.179 --> 00:14:31.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest, Commander, she seems...</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:14:32.338 --> 00:14:33.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interested in me.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:14:35.976 --> 00:14:37.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong with that?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:14:38.975 --> 00:14:40.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's extremely aggressive.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:14:40.775 --> 00:14:43.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see. So she's after you.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:14:44.542 --> 00:14:46.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like a Wanoni tracehound.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:14:46.573 --> 00:14:48.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you thought of letting her catch you?</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:14:49.373 --> 00:14:50.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir?</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:14:50.812 --> 00:14:52.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A little romance, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:14:53.118 --> 00:14:56.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have six pylons that need a complete</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>security sweep.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:14:56.650 --> 00:14:59.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have time for romantic interludes.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:15:03.448 --> 00:15:06.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Frankly, in my humble opinion,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>most of you humanoids</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:15:06.127 --> 00:15:10.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>spend far too much time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on your respective mating rituals.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:10.646 --> 00:15:12.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It does help the procreation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of one's species.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:13.646 --> 00:15:17.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Procreation does not require</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>changing how you smell</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:17.124 --> 00:15:21.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or writing bad poetry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or sacrificing various plants</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:15:21.123 --> 00:15:23.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to serve as tokens of affection.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:15:24.962 --> 00:15:27.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In any event,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's all irrelevant to me.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:15:28.159 --> 00:15:29.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry to hear that.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:15:30.599 --> 00:15:33.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would appreciate it if you would do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something about this woman.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:15:33.319 --> 00:15:34.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:15:34.399 --> 00:15:36.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just tell her to leave me alone.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:15:37.238 --> 00:15:40.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Constable, you can handle thieves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and killers, but not one Betazoid woman?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:15:41.277 --> 00:15:45.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand thieves and killers.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand... her.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:15:46.595 --> 00:15:48.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't help you, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:15:48.275 --> 00:15:51.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm just trying to avoid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a diplomatic incident.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:15:51.234 --> 00:15:52.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to insult the Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:15:53.193 --> 00:15:54.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: A reasonable concern.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:15:54.873 --> 00:15:57.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest you handle the matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with great delicacy.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:02.991 --> 00:16:06.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't handle "delicacy" very well.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:10.508 --> 00:16:13.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The probe appears to be made out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of some sort of corundium alloy.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:14.667 --> 00:16:17.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Analysis of all subprocessor</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>modules is complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

287
00:16:18.626 --> 00:16:19.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Already?</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:16:20.546 --> 00:16:21.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:16:23.265 --> 00:16:24.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:16:28.782 --> 00:16:31.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No science modules</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no communications system</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:16:32.223 --> 00:16:35.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and enough computer capacity to run</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a Galaxy-class starship.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:16:35.540 --> 00:16:36.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's very odd.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:16:37.261 --> 00:16:40.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's an awful lot of computer hardware</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>simply to navigate a probe.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:16:40.219 --> 00:16:41.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anything?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:16:42.192 --> 00:16:43.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing to suggest the probe's mission...</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:16:44.418 --> 00:16:46.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or any hint of its origin.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:16:54.175 --> 00:16:56.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah! There you are, Odo!</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:16:56.335 --> 00:17:00.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs ) Have you ever been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the fourth moon of Andevian II at dawn?</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:00.533 --> 00:17:02.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can't say I have.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:02.936 --> 00:17:05.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have the most wonderful holoprogram.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And I've reserved a suite for us</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:05.452 --> 00:17:06.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with that Quark person.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:07.131 --> 00:17:09.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told Quark that you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were going into a holosuite with me?</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:09.810 --> 00:17:10.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, of course.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:10.690 --> 00:17:12.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's preparing a special</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>picnic basket for us.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:12.770 --> 00:17:13.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good Lord.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:17:14.169 --> 00:17:15.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid I'm not available.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:17:15.529 --> 00:17:17.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to get</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to Upper Pylon 3 immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:17:17.848 --> 00:17:18.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador...</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:17:18.808 --> 00:17:19.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:17:20.448 --> 00:17:22.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um... Upper Pylon 3.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:17:22.846 --> 00:17:25.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've always wanted to see an upper pylon.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:17:27.925 --> 00:17:31.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, I'll have Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>send one of his minions with our basket.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:17:31.804 --> 00:17:33.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll have our picnic up there.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:17:33.164 --> 00:17:34.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador...</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:17:34.283 --> 00:17:36.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:17:36.122 --> 00:17:39.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't eat. This is not a real mouth.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:17:40.183 --> 00:17:44.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is an approximation of one.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I do not have an esophagus or a stomach</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:17:44.600 --> 00:17:47.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or a digestive system. I am not like you.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:17:47.799 --> 00:17:52.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every 16 hours, I turn into a liquid.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:17:53.117 --> 00:17:54.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can swim.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:17:54.237 --> 00:17:55.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:17:59.196 --> 00:18:00.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer?</c.bg_transparent>

