00:18:01.355 --> 00:18:02.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer!</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:18:04.874 --> 00:18:05.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:18:06.273 --> 00:18:07.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

326
