332
00:18:25.948 --> 00:18:27.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Energizing.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:18:33.226 --> 00:18:34.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well?</c.bg_transparent>

334
