335
00:18:36.424 --> 00:18:37.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>But don't worry, Constable.</i></c.bg_transparent>

336
00:18:37.784 --> 00:18:39.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
