338
00:18:43.982 --> 00:18:44.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be patient, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:18:44.862 --> 00:18:46.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll get you out of there</i></c.bg_transparent>
