<c.bg_transparent><i>Diagnostic complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

344
00:19:14.293 --> 00:19:15.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't get it.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:19:16.526 --> 00:19:19.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
