357
00:19:44.846 --> 00:19:45.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I knew.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:19:47.243 --> 00:19:49.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>By the way, Cardassian turbolifts</i></c.bg_transparent>

