363
00:19:59.919 --> 00:20:01.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, it wouldn't be polite.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:20:02.392 --> 00:20:03.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I didn't hear that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

365
00:20:05.318 --> 00:20:06.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--It wouldn't be polite.</c.bg_transparent>

366
