368
00:20:13.675 --> 00:20:16.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you suppose that we're, uh...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're actually in any danger?</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:20:17.674 --> 00:20:19.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not if we remain calm.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:20:19.553 --> 00:20:20.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:20:21.433 --> 00:20:24.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, then we might as well</c.bg_transparent>
