<c.bg_transparent>I'd really prefer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to pass the time quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:20:33.589 --> 00:20:34.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:20:34.709 --> 00:20:35.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:20:35.909 --> 00:20:36.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:20:42.306 --> 00:20:43.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:20:44.346 --> 00:20:45.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The quiet man.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:20:46.305 --> 00:20:47.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:20:48.185 --> 00:20:51.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've always been attracted to quiet men.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:20:51.784 --> 00:20:52.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odd, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:20:53.543 --> 00:20:57.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But maybe there's more truth than</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we realize to that old axiom that op--</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:21:00.381 --> 00:21:01.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:21:12.186 --> 00:21:12.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:21:14.657 --> 00:21:15.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:21:16.657 --> 00:21:17.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think I can.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:21:20.975 --> 00:21:22.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can what?</c.bg_transparent>

388
