<c.bg_transparent>but I, I think I really need to talk.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:21:31.172 --> 00:21:31.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:21:34.571 --> 00:21:35.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:21:41.497 --> 00:21:42.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing to be afraid of.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:21:43.890 --> 00:21:44.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course not.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:21:44.728 --> 00:21:47.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, things could be much worse.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:21:47.767 --> 00:21:48.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really?</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:21:48.646 --> 00:21:50.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:21:50.206 --> 00:21:52.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My daughter and I were once trapped</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:21:52.286 --> 00:21:54.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
