402
00:22:03.442 --> 00:22:04.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well...</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:22:04.402 --> 00:22:07.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, he wasn't altogether loathsome.</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:22:07.122 --> 00:22:09.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was just slightly repulsive.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:22:10.281 --> 00:22:16.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he did have a certain charm</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in an insufferable kind of way.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:22:17.478 --> 00:22:21.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, he was totally at the mercy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his uncontrollable passion for me</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:22:21.597 --> 00:22:24.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>which means he wasn't all bad,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>now, doesn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:22:25.316 --> 00:22:27.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you know, it wasn't all passion, no.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:22:28.353 --> 00:22:31.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was some negligible</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>commercial interest involved</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:22:31.754 --> 00:22:36.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, oh, the passion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>oh, that was... that was perfectly real</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:22:37.323 --> 00:22:39.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and kind of, um, kind of sweet in a way.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:22:40.751 --> 00:22:42.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was so helpless.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:22:42.871 --> 00:22:45.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At first, it was totally</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a question of expediency</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:22:46.705 --> 00:22:48.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I made love with--with him.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:22:48.509 --> 00:22:49.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you looking at?</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:22:50.788 --> 00:22:51.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:22:51.948 --> 00:22:52.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:22:52.827 --> 00:22:53.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:22:53.987 --> 00:22:54.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:22:55.667 --> 00:23:00.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just wondering how many volts</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are in that exposed circuit.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:23:01.145 --> 00:23:02.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on. Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:23:03.185 --> 00:23:06.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... frankly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the time one thing led to another...</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:23:08.823 --> 00:23:12.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of it as an opportunity, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You never know when a friendly ambassador</c.bg_transparent>

424
