<c.bg_transparent>is going to be in the right place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the right time to help your career.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:23:15.261 --> 00:23:18.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Another hour with them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could destroy my career.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:23:18.420 --> 00:23:22.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a simple job.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just keep them happy and away from me.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:23:22.138 --> 00:23:22.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Simple?</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:23:23.378 --> 00:23:24.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing makes them happy.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:23:25.618 --> 00:23:27.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are dedicated to being unhappy</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:23:27.737 --> 00:23:29.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to spreading that unhappiness</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wherever they go.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:23:29.937 --> 00:23:32.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are the Ambassadors of Unhappy.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:23:32.735 --> 00:23:34.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:23:34.215 --> 00:23:35.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of us have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>had these assignments, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:23:35.975 --> 00:23:36.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:23:36.935 --> 00:23:40.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a matter of fact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax used to take perverse pleasure</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:23:40.943 --> 00:23:41.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in assigning me to take care</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of VIP guests.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:23:42.333 --> 00:23:45.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, so now you take the same</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>perverse pleasure.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:23:45.171 --> 00:23:46.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In doing it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:23:46.772 --> 00:23:47.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:23:48.651 --> 00:23:49.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I ask, sir</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:23:49.610 --> 00:23:52.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when you graduated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from this sort of assignment?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:23:55.328 --> 00:23:57.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The day I hit one of the guests.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:23:58.568 --> 00:23:59.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hit one...</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:24:00.488 --> 00:24:03.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a simple misunderstanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>over his attempt to coax a young Ensign</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:24:03.606 --> 00:24:05.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to his quarters against her will.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:24:07.605 --> 00:24:08.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But...</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:24:10.724 --> 00:24:12.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't hit one of them, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:24:12.444 --> 00:24:14.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not nearly as understanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as Curzon was.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:24:15.403 --> 00:24:16.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:24:17.642 --> 00:24:19.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'Brien: Commander, can I talk to you?</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:24:23.281 --> 00:24:26.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's about the computer, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Still giving you problems?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:24:26.120 --> 00:24:28.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, sir, that's just the thing, it's not.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:24:28.119 --> 00:24:30.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It rerouted the EPS power flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in less than an hour.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:24:30.598 --> 00:24:31.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's good news.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:24:31.838 --> 00:24:33.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How soon can we get Odo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the Ambassador out?</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:24:33.958 --> 00:24:36.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It didn't activate the turbolift circuits.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:24:36.876 --> 00:24:38.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't ask me why.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:24:38.316 --> 00:24:40.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must have some idea of what's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:24:40.915 --> 00:24:42.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to listen to something.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:24:42.914 --> 00:24:47.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze Ops 0-2 sensor readings.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:24:48.433 --> 00:24:53.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>All sensors read between 14.3</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and 14.4 KSC.</i></c.bg_transparent>

462
00:24:57.670 --> 00:25:01.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, restart all shield</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>generator subsystems.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:25:02.269 --> 00:25:04.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Shield generator subsystems</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>set to active status.</i></c.bg_transparent>

464
00:25:05.686 --> 00:25:07.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Reading 98.3% efficiency.</i></c.bg_transparent>

465
00:25:07.987 --> 00:25:09.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) Do you hear it?</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:25:11.746 --> 00:25:12.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) Hear what?</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:25:13.656 --> 00:25:15.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The voice, it's not the same attitude.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:25:15.544 --> 00:25:17.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds like the computer.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:25:17.864 --> 00:25:19.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, when you work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a computer as much as I do</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:25:20.242 --> 00:25:22.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you get to know it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're all very different.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:25:22.822 --> 00:25:25.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Working with the</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was like dancing a waltz.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:25:25.941 --> 00:25:28.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With this computer, it's always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>been like a wrestling match</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:25:28.701 --> 00:25:30.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>till we started downloading the probe.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:25:30.820 --> 00:25:32.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think some kind of program</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the probe</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:25:32.780 --> 00:25:34.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is influencing our computer?</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:25:34.539 --> 00:25:36.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it's got to be more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than just a program, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:25:36.938 --> 00:25:39.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer's whole personality</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has changed.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:25:39.898 --> 00:25:41.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not resisting any commands</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:25:42.574 --> 00:25:44.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>offering any opinions,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>giving any arguments</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:25:45.816 --> 00:25:49.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there's this one other crazy thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm almost afraid to mention.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:25:49.495 --> 00:25:50.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:25:50.974 --> 00:25:54.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every time I leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something happens to bring me back.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:25:54.293 --> 00:25:55.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring you back?</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:25:55.653 --> 00:26:00.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To the computer like the failures</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the turbolifts and the transporters.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:26:00.212 --> 00:26:02.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few minutes ago, I was working</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the transporter pad</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:26:02.290 --> 00:26:06.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the com lines went down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and when I broke for a quick bite to eat</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:26:06.490 --> 00:26:07.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we had a replicator failure.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:26:08.409 --> 00:26:11.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's almost like the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doesn't want me to leave it alone.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:26:12.368 --> 00:26:14.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You almost make it sound like a child.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:26:24.479 --> 00:26:25.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

491
00:26:26.379 --> 00:26:29.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo and Ambassador Troi</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>remain trapped in Turbolift 4.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:26:29.442 --> 00:26:32.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>As of yet, we have been unable</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to ascertain what it is</i></c.bg_transparent>

493
00:26:32.321 --> 00:26:35.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that's causing the station's computer</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to malfunction.</i></c.bg_transparent>

494
00:26:35.761 --> 00:26:38.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it's some kind</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of non biological life-form</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:26:38.560 --> 00:26:39.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we've never seen before?</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:26:39.800 --> 00:26:40.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nonbiological?</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:26:41.519 --> 00:26:44.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it all comes down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to how we define life-form.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:26:44.518 --> 00:26:48.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But just as biological organisms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have evolved in our cultures</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:26:48.117 --> 00:26:50.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>mechanical life could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have done the same in others.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:26:51.196 --> 00:26:54.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're suggesting someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>left a baby at our doorstep.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:26:54.715 --> 00:26:55.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Possibly.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:26:55.835 --> 00:26:57.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you think we can communicate with it?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:26:57.594 --> 00:26:59.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, in a way, we already have.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:26:59.313 --> 00:27:01.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, it's part and parcel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of our computer now.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:27:01.593 --> 00:27:03.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But as far as direct communication</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is concerned</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:27:03.912 --> 00:27:05.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it may not be capable of that.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:27:05.432 --> 00:27:07.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We haven't seen any evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that this entity is sentient.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:27:07.711 --> 00:27:11.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Maybe more like a stray puppy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's attached itself to you, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:27:11.390 --> 00:27:13.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whatever it is, it's slowly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>disabling our station.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:27:13.429 --> 00:27:15.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>People, we've got to get it out of there.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:27:15.709 --> 00:27:19.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It came here when we downloaded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the probe's files.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:27:19.347 --> 00:27:23.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we upload those same files back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the probe it might go with them.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:27:23.466 --> 00:27:25.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it's fully integrated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>itself into our computer?</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:27:25.946 --> 00:27:29.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think it has.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That would make it more like a virus.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:27:29.425 --> 00:27:32.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I don't see any evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that it's trying to overwrite</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:27:32.424 --> 00:27:34.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>our control networks or destroy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>our systems.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:27:34.544 --> 00:27:37.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's more likely that it simply</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>creates connections</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:27:37.543 --> 00:27:39.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with areas of the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that are active.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:27:39.221 --> 00:27:42.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Almost as though it feeds off the energy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the computer functions.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:27:42.500 --> 00:27:45.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I'm right, transferring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all of its programming</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:27:45.220 --> 00:27:47.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>off the station might just solve</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>our problems.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:27:52.338 --> 00:27:55.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long since we had any communication</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Odo?</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:27:55.137 --> 00:27:59.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Com lines have been down over 90 minutes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's been in there almost four hours now.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:28:00.215 --> 00:28:03.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you happen to know the schedule</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his regenerative cycle?</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:28:03.415 --> 00:28:04.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My God, I have no idea</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:28:06.938 --> 00:28:08.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but if he doesn't get back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to his pail in time...</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:28:16.131 --> 00:28:20.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Subspace emitter aligned.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Outgoing data stream activated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

528
00:28:21.494 --> 00:28:24.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, upload</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:28:24.528 --> 00:28:26.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>back to probe's computer.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:28:26.608 --> 00:28:27.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:28:28.127 --> 00:28:32.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Unable to complete requested function.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please abort and retry.</i></c.bg_transparent>

532
00:28:33.286 --> 00:28:35.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reset subspace emitter.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:28:36.284 --> 00:28:38.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reinitialize data stream.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:28:39.442 --> 00:28:42.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Receptors open. Control relays activated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

535
00:28:44.432 --> 00:28:48.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Upload all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back to probe's computers.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:28:48.481 --> 00:28:49.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

537
00:28:54.679 --> 00:28:57.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not as easy as I thought</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it would be, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:29:00.758 --> 00:29:04.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is it just the lights or the heat, too?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't bring any warm clothes.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:29:04.916 --> 00:29:06.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure it's just temporary.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:29:07.756 --> 00:29:11.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been reading the reports</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your Chief of Operations, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:29:11.674 --> 00:29:14.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me the impression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that he was a competent engineer.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:29:15.732 --> 00:29:17.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>One of the best in Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:29:17.872 --> 00:29:19.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why aren't the backup</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>systems functioning?</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:29:20.551 --> 00:29:21.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you know...</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:29:21.871 --> 00:29:26.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Out here on the edge of the frontier</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's just one adventure after another.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:29:26.830 --> 00:29:29.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't I escort you all back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your quarters,</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:29:29.509 --> 00:29:33.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>where I'm sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can all wait this one out.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:29:43.584 --> 00:29:44.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But enough about me.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:29:46.544 --> 00:29:47.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:29:47.903 --> 00:29:50.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough about me. Tell me about yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:29:53.217 --> 00:29:54.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm really a private man.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:29:56.581 --> 00:29:57.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, of course you are.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:30:01.579 --> 00:30:02.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that hair real?</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:30:05.538 --> 00:30:07.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is real in that it is me.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:30:08.897 --> 00:30:10.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is not real hair.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:30:12.165 --> 00:30:12.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did you do it?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:30:13.416 --> 00:30:14.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your hair.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:30:16.735 --> 00:30:18.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It took a great deal of practice.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:30:19.454 --> 00:30:20.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You studied hairstyles?</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:30:21.853 --> 00:30:22.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:30:24.527 --> 00:30:27.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you must know I imitated the hairstyle</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:30:27.651 --> 00:30:29.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of the Bajoran man who was assigned to me.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:30:31.506 --> 00:30:31.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Assigned?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:30:33.450 --> 00:30:38.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To study me at the research center.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He was a scientist.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:30:39.328 --> 00:30:43.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean that's how you grew up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a laboratory?</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:30:44.326 --> 00:30:47.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did not grow up as you think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:30:48.285 --> 00:30:51.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was merely a transition</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from what I used to be...</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:30:52.963 --> 00:30:54.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To what I learned to become.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:30:55.962 --> 00:30:56.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:30:59.362 --> 00:31:01.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds very lonely to me.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:31:04.760 --> 00:31:06.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was always very self-sufficient.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:31:08.759 --> 00:31:12.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure you had to be...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>uh, to survive...</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:31:12.837 --> 00:31:15.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being... being so different</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from everyone else.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:31:19.596 --> 00:31:20.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:31:21.275 --> 00:31:22.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:31:23.435 --> 00:31:24.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Com lines are still down.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:31:25.434 --> 00:31:27.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what's taking so long.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:31:27.553 --> 00:31:29.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure you're all right?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You look warm.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:31:30.331 --> 00:31:31.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's nothing. I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:31:35.714 --> 00:31:37.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I can't imagine how it must have been.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:31:38.710 --> 00:31:41.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, if it bothers you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to talk about this...</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:31:41.310 --> 00:31:42.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:31:44.588 --> 00:31:45.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was it like?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:31:45.948 --> 00:31:49.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess you could say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was the life of the party.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:31:50.187 --> 00:31:52.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:31:52.546 --> 00:31:54.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My way of trying to fit in.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:31:55.225 --> 00:31:57.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I found I could be entertaining.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:31:57.905 --> 00:32:01.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Odo, be a chair." I'm a chair.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>"Odo, be a razorcat." I'm a razorcat.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:32:01.743 --> 00:32:03.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Life of the party.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:32:03.503 --> 00:32:04.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:32:05.262 --> 00:32:07.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hate parties.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:32:09.300 --> 00:32:11.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, perhaps you've been going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the wrong ones.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:32:14.220 --> 00:32:15.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come to one of mine, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:32:16.993 --> 00:32:19.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make sure that all the guests</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are there to entertain you.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:32:23.537 --> 00:32:24.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:32:24.777 --> 00:32:26.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, now, you're not well.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:32:27.415 --> 00:32:28.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, it's fine. It's just, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:32:32.934 --> 00:32:36.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you I turn into a liquid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every 16 hours.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:32:38.692 --> 00:32:41.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm in hour 15.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:32:50.768 --> 00:32:51.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ready, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:32:51.928 --> 00:32:53.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long do you expect it to take?</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:32:53.767 --> 00:32:54.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if it works</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:32:54.727 --> 00:32:56.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we ought to be able</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get all the probe's files</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:32:56.407 --> 00:32:58.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>manually transferred</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the six isolinear rods</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:32:58.686 --> 00:32:59.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in less than 60 seconds.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:32:59.966 --> 00:33:00.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's do it.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:33:02.547 --> 00:33:06.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, run a level-1 diagnostic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of all power systems on board.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:33:06.284 --> 00:33:08.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Requested function</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>will require 43 minutes.</i></c.bg_transparent>

609
00:33:08.923 --> 00:33:09.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:33:11.962 --> 00:33:14.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Computer, give me an analysis</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:33:14.522 --> 00:33:16.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of all Cardassian traffic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>along the border.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:33:17.809 --> 00:33:19.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Processing long-range sensors. Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

613
00:33:21.599 --> 00:33:24.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Computer create</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a historical data base</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:33:24.399 --> 00:33:25.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for all known wormhole activity.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:33:26.478 --> 00:33:28.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( stuttering )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Indicate time parameters.</i></c.bg_transparent>

616
00:33:28.837 --> 00:33:30.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: All known occurrences.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:33:30.717 --> 00:33:35.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( slowly )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Requested function</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>will require subspace link-up.</i></c.bg_transparent>

618
00:33:35.555 --> 00:33:39.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: In that case, create a subspace</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>link with Nehru Colony,</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:33:39.513 --> 00:33:43.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>New France Colony,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Corado I Transmitter Array.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:33:43.993 --> 00:33:48.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( stuttering )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Attempting link-up.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by...</i></c.bg_transparent>

621
00:33:50.110 --> 00:33:53.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, access musical files</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Bajor Master Data Banks</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:33:53.669 --> 00:33:56.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and create a concert program</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Bajoran serenas.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:33:56.269 --> 00:33:59.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand... by...</i></c.bg_transparent>

624
00:33:59.748 --> 00:34:03.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( fading )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Unable to...</i></c.bg_transparent>

625
00:34:04.266 --> 00:34:05.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand...</i></c.bg_transparent>

626
00:34:08.146 --> 00:34:10.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading a huge plasma surge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Habitat Ring.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:34:11.464 --> 00:34:13.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You tell Commander Sisko that I expect</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that probe briefing</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:34:13.823 --> 00:34:16.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be held on schedule,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lights or no lights.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:34:16.702 --> 00:34:18.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will surely pass that on, Ambassador--</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:34:22.700 --> 00:34:25.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got a plasma explosion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in corridor H-12-A, guest quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:34:25.859 --> 00:34:27.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer's not responding.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:34:27.996 --> 00:34:29.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>None of the fire suppression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>systems are coming on line.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:34:29.219 --> 00:34:30.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading four life-forms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that corridor.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:34:30.899 --> 00:34:33.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, you're with me. Chief,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>get an emergency crew down there.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:34:33.417 --> 00:34:35.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We'll need manual fire gear.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:34:35.377 --> 00:34:37.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:34:51.732 --> 00:34:55.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:35:11.726 --> 00:35:13.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Phasers at maximum.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:35:18.684 --> 00:35:21.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Toranium inlay, Cardassian design</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I should have guessed.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:35:21.163 --> 00:35:23.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're going to need a bipolar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>torch to get through it.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:35:23.442 --> 00:35:24.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then get a message to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:35:24.762 --> 00:35:26.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell them it's going to take us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a while to get inside.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:35:26.761 --> 00:35:28.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If they can't get the fire</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>suppression systems on line</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:35:28.841 --> 00:35:30.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we're going to lose our people in there.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:35:30.160 --> 00:35:31.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:35:33.801 --> 00:35:35.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not paying any attention to me.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:35:36.359 --> 00:35:40.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess it just doesn't want to leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like a scared puppy.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:35:41.377 --> 00:35:45.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have no idea how long that probe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was tumbling through space, maybe years,</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:35:45.236 --> 00:35:47.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with that life-form alone on board.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:35:47.556 --> 00:35:50.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's sort of like shutting up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a puppy in a room, you know?</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:35:51.749 --> 00:35:53.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a pup once. If I had to lock him up</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:35:53.793 --> 00:35:56.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'd scratch forever</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the door trying to get out.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:35:56.433 --> 00:35:58.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure I know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you're getting at.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:35:58.712 --> 00:36:01.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pups don't like to be left alone.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They like attention.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:36:02.471 --> 00:36:04.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This one is certainly getting a lot of it.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:36:04.870 --> 00:36:05.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:36:06.550 --> 00:36:08.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So it's no wonder</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it doesn't want to leave.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:36:09.295 --> 00:36:11.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>OK, but how is that going to help us?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:36:11.428 --> 00:36:12.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything we've seen suggests</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:36:12.868 --> 00:36:15.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that this entity likes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be where the action is.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:36:15.827 --> 00:36:18.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems to feed off the energy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of an active computer.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:36:18.746 --> 00:36:21.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've been trying to separate it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from what it thrives on.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:36:22.385 --> 00:36:24.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to do the exact opposite.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:36:24.664 --> 00:36:25.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The exact opposite?</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:36:26.184 --> 00:36:29.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant, I've got to build a doghouse.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:36:30.822 --> 00:36:34.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( labored breathing )</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:36:40.300 --> 00:36:41.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:36:42.818 --> 00:36:43.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:36:47.178 --> 00:36:47.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo out.</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:36:48.617 --> 00:36:50.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo, turn around.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:36:51.565 --> 00:36:53.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't. It's beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:36:54.935 --> 00:36:56.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:36:57.335 --> 00:36:58.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:36:59.814 --> 00:37:02.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one has ever seen me like this before.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:37:03.613 --> 00:37:05.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not even the scientist</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who was assigned to you?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:37:06.411 --> 00:37:07.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was different.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:37:08.172 --> 00:37:09.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was only research to him.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:37:11.530 --> 00:37:13.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you don't have to be ashamed with me.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:37:14.369 --> 00:37:15.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not ashamed.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:37:17.209 --> 00:37:19.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a private matter, that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:37:22.795 --> 00:37:24.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How can I make it easier for you?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:37:25.366 --> 00:37:26.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:37:27.462 --> 00:37:27.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:37:36.442 --> 00:37:37.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:37:38.242 --> 00:37:39.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My hair.</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:37:48.793 --> 00:37:50.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one's ever seen me like this.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:37:52.518 --> 00:37:53.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:37:55.379 --> 00:37:56.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It looks fine.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:37:58.396 --> 00:37:59.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It looks ordinary.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:38:00.595 --> 00:38:02.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never cared to be ordinary.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:38:04.554 --> 00:38:07.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you see, Odo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even we non-shape-shifters</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:38:07.514 --> 00:38:09.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>have to change who we are once in a while.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:38:12.432 --> 00:38:15.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are not at all what I expected.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:38:19.307 --> 00:38:21.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one's ever paid me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a greater compliment.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:38:29.346 --> 00:38:34.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... cannot hold my shape any longer.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:38:37.304 --> 00:38:38.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let go.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:38:40.944 --> 00:38:42.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll take care of you.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:38:42.583 --> 00:38:44.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:38:51.340 --> 00:38:54.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: We're going to need portable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>oxygen and get anything</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:38:54.899 --> 00:38:57.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bashir has in stock to treat plasma burns.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Have a runabout ready</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:38:57.979 --> 00:38:59.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to evacuate these people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to Bajor if we need to.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:38:59.698 --> 00:39:00.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:39:03.617 --> 00:39:04.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anara?</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:39:05.136 --> 00:39:06.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The subprogram is ready, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:39:07.735 --> 00:39:11.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze subprogram</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>labeled "Pup."</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:39:12.546 --> 00:39:15.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Requested subprogram is a series</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of bi-directional data transfer</i></c.bg_transparent>

707
00:39:15.813 --> 00:39:17.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>and monitoring commands.</i></c.bg_transparent>

708
00:39:17.492 --> 00:39:21.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reroute all main computer backup functions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through this subprogram.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:39:22.331 --> 00:39:24.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>All backup functions rerouted.</i></c.bg_transparent>

710
00:39:24.970 --> 00:39:25.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Great.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:39:26.929 --> 00:39:28.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>OK, computer. Now, listen carefully.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:39:29.449 --> 00:39:32.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to transfer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:39:32.528 --> 00:39:35.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>out of core memory</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and into the subprogram Pup.</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:39:35.767 --> 00:39:37.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

715
00:39:39.867 --> 00:39:40.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Transfer complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

716
00:39:42.565 --> 00:39:45.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dax to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Fire suppression is responding.</i></c.bg_transparent>

717
00:39:45.565 --> 00:39:47.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>All systems are back on line.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Can you get in?</i></c.bg_transparent>

718
00:39:51.723 --> 00:39:53.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're in, Dax. Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:39:55.601 --> 00:39:58.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electrical hissing and popping )</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:40:14.764 --> 00:40:16.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'd better advise Starfleet Command.</c.bg_transparent>

721
00:40:17.154 --> 00:40:18.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rattling )</c.bg_transparent>

722
00:40:21.993 --> 00:40:23.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

723
00:40:23.992 --> 00:40:25.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Here, take my hand,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

724
00:40:26.832 --> 00:40:27.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Watch your head.</c.bg_transparent>

725
00:40:29.911 --> 00:40:30.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

726
00:40:31.430 --> 00:40:32.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Call me Taxco.</c.bg_transparent>

727
00:40:34.429 --> 00:40:35.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ambassador, are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

728
00:40:35.829 --> 00:40:37.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes. Thanks to Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

729
00:40:41.827 --> 00:40:44.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Doctor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was remarkably calm and logical,</c.bg_transparent>

730
00:40:44.986 --> 00:40:48.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for a man of his years,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>under such severe conditions.</c.bg_transparent>

731
00:40:48.545 --> 00:40:50.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be putting him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in for a commendation.</c.bg_transparent>

732
00:40:55.143 --> 00:40:56.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nice work, Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

733
00:40:57.663 --> 00:41:00.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just in the right place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the right time, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

734
00:41:07.179 --> 00:41:09.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it's about time.</c.bg_transparent>

735
00:41:11.779 --> 00:41:16.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... know that wasn't exactly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you had in mind</c.bg_transparent>

736
00:41:16.937 --> 00:41:17.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for your picnic.</c.bg_transparent>

737
00:41:19.896 --> 00:41:23.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When it comes to picnics</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the only thing that really matters</c.bg_transparent>

738
00:41:23.175 --> 00:41:24.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is the company.</c.bg_transparent>

739
00:41:25.574 --> 00:41:29.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your sensitivity and discretion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are appreciated.</c.bg_transparent>

740
00:41:30.813 --> 00:41:31.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well...</c.bg_transparent>

741
00:41:33.692 --> 00:41:36.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next time you see me I'll give you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a lot more to appreciate.</c.bg_transparent>

742
00:41:49.207 --> 00:41:51.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did you beat that thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the computer, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

743
00:41:52.466 --> 00:41:54.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I didn't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He adopted it.</c.bg_transparent>

744
00:41:54.446 --> 00:41:55.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Adopted it?</c.bg_transparent>

745
00:41:55.406 --> 00:41:56.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I was able to get our friend</c.bg_transparent>

746
00:41:56.644 --> 00:41:58.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>out of the main command pathways</c.bg_transparent>
